\n出黎隻揪</blockquote><br />\n我識九頭龍閃"},{"pid":"73ebbef272fe3293817f0c837cce22459bb4f093","tid":475481,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本成日都有兒童AV買。<br />\n不過佢哋會偷偷地囉，<br />\n可能淨係做熟客生意。</blockquote><br />\n有好多都係偽蘿莉</blockquote><br />\n有真野架，偽蘿莉唔使偷偷賣。</blockquote><br />\n因為拍而D偷偷賣都賣到唔少錢<br />\n之前有單就係有條友係咁拍自己個女拎去賣,賺左起碼幾百萬日元<br />\n比人捉左"},{"pid":"2dac898cbd76283bf2a8c80a4ef8c4814be8eed8","tid":475481,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d48668a93be7f75180dcecb60ec493c1f04b970","tid":475481,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"唔睇cp唔會畫得咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2b1759e82a7e170c8a86dac88741c53d5acd2d","tid":475481,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"搵我？"},{"pid":"27886f68c6abf973c4beb3a75ec15e90ca18ec02","tid":475481,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"【違反兒童色情法】《浪客劍心》作者和月伸宏 持女童裸露影片被送檢<br />\n<br />\n人氣漫畫《浪客劍心》作者和月伸宏因持有女童裸體DVD，涉違反兒童賣春、兒童色情禁止法，案件已被日本警方送檢。<br />\n<br />\n警方到和月伸宏辦公室及寓所搜查時，發現不少10至15歲嘅未成年少女裸露影片，佢亦承認「喜歡小學高年級到中二年級左右的女孩。」日本法律規定，持有未成年兒童色情影片面臨被處以1年以下徒刑，或罰款100萬日圓（約7萬港）。<br />\n和月伸宏現年47歲，其著作《浪客劍心》大受漫畫迷歡迎，曾被改編成動畫同拍成真人版電影，今年秋天《浪客劍心》先開始喺《Jump SQ》重新連載，所以佢涉違反兒童色情法被送檢，令唔少漫畫迷相當震驚，集英社方面亦決定停止《浪客劍心》嘅連載。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171121/57485904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57485904&d=zW8s0yBelm5wq9enpmvRSP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4830124d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57485904&h=6ca2d0ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171121/57485904</a>"}]}